mathematics /ˌmæθəˈmætɪks/

1. N-UNCOUNT Mathematics is the study of numbers, quantities, or shapes. 数学 

例： ...a professor of mathematics at Boston College. …一位波士顿大学的数学教授。 

2. N-UNCOUNT The mathematics of a problem is the calculations that are involved in it. 数学运算 

